I was born and raised in California. I have never lived in Iran and the last time I visited I was only 4 years old. But my love for the culture and where I come from runs through my veins. 
You often see me cooking, dancing and speaking in Persian as I fight to keep my
Culture alive for my kids and the generation who may not know the Iran our parents know. And now I found a way to bring our cultures even closer together. Through food, dance, laughter and LOVE we are excited to announce the coming of a new cooking show
 ✨BEREEZ-O-BEPAZ ba Shally✨
airing on Voice of America beginning late October. 
This kitchen is for dancing. And from it we create LOVE that we are packaging up and sending to you soon! 💜
@voafarsi @samanism so so excited! Let the magic begin! 
✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨
من توی کالیفرنیا به دنیا اومدم و همینجا بزرگ شدم و هیچوقت توی ایران زندگی نکردم، آخرین باری که ایران بودم ۴ سالم بود. ولی عاشق ایران ‌و فرهنگ ایران هستم و قلبم برای جایی که ازش اومدم میزنه. 
همه سعی‌ام رو کردم که با رقص، آشپزی و حرف زدن فرهنگ ایران رو برای بچه‌هام و کسانی که شاید کمتر با فرهنگ ایران آشنایی دارن نشون بدم و زنده نگه‌اش دارم. 
 آشپزی، رقص، شادی و خنده بهانه‌ای هست که در این روزهای سخت، عشق رو به خونه‌های شما بیاریم. 
“ بریز و بپز با شالی”
اواسط پاییز در کانال صدای آمریکا. 
شما هم میهمان آشپزخانه من باشید. 
@voafarsi @samanism
بزن و بریم
#voapersian #persian #bereezobepaz #shallyzomorodi
And btw @naserzeynalii LOVE ur songs!!!

You have done so much work in the arena of anti-bullying and I am grateful for your support. Parents. I hope you find a moment to listen to her and this session. It will change your children’s lives. 
🦋 our pick-up event for today the book is now FULL. You can pre- order the book and doll on my website www.SHALLZ..com
So grateful for your love
And support

A few years ago after I decided to write a book I had the idea to find the illustrator through a search on social media. I received hundreds and hundreds of emails. Having a hard time picking someone I mentioned to my mom I was struggling and wish I could give everyone a chance. And that’s when everything changed. She told me I have a cousin in Iran who is an incredible artist and could possibly do it. 
And she did. We haven’t sent each other in more than 4 decades. She is my family. My cousin. And now the illustrator of my first book. 
@azi.cake1 I LOVE YOU! Thank you for helping me make my dreams come true. I pray for the day I can hold you and squeeze you again. 
ASHEGETAM AZI jooooon! 🦋
Today is the final day to pre-order you book and pick it up at a special event in SOCAL. Order yours at www.SHALLZ.com

NEW SESSION And a must watch! 
Who are emotional vampires? Are they part of some strange cult or horror movie? Unfortunately not - many live amongst us! They are called emotional vampires because their actions and attitudes tend to drain the emotional energy out of different people they come in contact with. They can be psychologically exhausting due to their need for constant attention and crisis. Join me and Dr. Shaheem on this segment as we discuss ways to better understand them and establish boundaries to protect our own emotional well-being 🧠🧛🏻‍♂️ @drshaheem #morethanmind #mentalhealth 
🎧 you can also find segment on my YouTube channel. And take us on the go via audio version on my podcast channel.

I was born and raised in California. I have never lived in Iran and the last time I visited I was only 4 years old. But my love for the culture and where I come from runs through my veins. 
You often see me cooking, dancing and speaking in Persian as I fight to keep my
Culture alive for my kids and the generation who may not know the Iran our parents know. And now I found a way to bring our cultures even closer together. Through food, dance, laughter and LOVE we are excited to announce the coming of a new cooking show
 ✨BEREEZ-O-BEPAZ ba Shally✨
airing on Voice of America beginning late October. 
This kitchen is for dancing. And from it we create LOVE that we are packaging up and sending to you soon! 💜
@voafarsi @samanism so so excited! Let the magic begin! 
✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨✨
من توی کالیفرنیا به دنیا اومدم و همینجا بزرگ شدم و هیچوقت توی ایران زندگی نکردم، آخرین باری که ایران بودم ۴ سالم بود. ولی عاشق ایران ‌و فرهنگ ایران هستم و قلبم برای جایی که ازش اومدم میزنه. 
همه سعی‌ام رو کردم که با رقص، آشپزی و حرف زدن فرهنگ ایران رو برای بچه‌هام و کسانی که شاید کمتر با فرهنگ ایران آشنایی دارن نشون بدم و زنده نگه‌اش دارم.

We brought 4 beautiful souls into this world and I am so incredible grateful for you and our family. What was. Still is. And lastly to my girls @beautybymelina @azi_fairysecret turning this mama who has not slept into a butterfly today 🦋

Myla is here 💜🦋
Just a few days ago my family and friends stood by my side as I released my first book ‘Myla Caterpillars become butterflies 🦋’
And TOMORROW I am finally going to meet some of you!!!! 
If you pre-ordered your book you should have received an email with the event location and time for tomorrow. This is a private event just for those who pre-ordered. 
I look forward to meeting you 🦋💜
📷: a special thank you to @navidstudio for this video capturing one magical day in my life. 
🦋 Myla. It’s now time to work your magic. All profits from this book in next few weeks will go to young women in Afghanistan 🦋 we begin shipping next week. You can order your book and doll at www.shallz.com

My dearest husband, it is your birthday today. I wanted to wish you the very best, but you already have me. No need 🤣🤣🤣

My Brucie. I know you aren’t the biggest fan of celebrating your birthday but I want to spoil the man who stole my ❤️. The man who shows up for our family everyday. The best daddy who adores his kids. The man with a heart of gold and one of the kindest people I know. And not to mention the man who puts up with me everyday 😉 I love growing old with you. Happy birthday to my Brucie. May all your dreams and wishes come true 🥳 #birthdayboy #happybirthday 
📸: @navidstudio
